  "title": "Auth HTTP Posture And GitHub Feedback Closure Task Packet",
  "goal": "Harden browser auth and HTTP posture in `pantheon-base`, add GitHub feedback closure automation for solo PR flow, and preserve the already-validated permission remediation compatibility fix bundled in this branch.",
